spell_tooltip.description: Increases Item Level by 5 and increases the potency of all Azerite powers granted by this item.
Exhilaration heals you for an additional 352 health, and the cooldown is reduced by 15.0 sec.
Your damaging abilities have a chance to deal 34 Physical damage to the target. Gutripper occurs much more often against targets below 30% health.
Barbed Shot deals 74 additional damage over its duration, and Frenzy's duration is increased to 9.0 sec.
Aspect of the Wild increases your Mastery by 60, and grants you a charge of Barbed Shot.
